OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,FA 71-year-old stroke patient suffered
OL,7,Fneglect during the junior doctors
OL,8,Fstrike which "contributed to her
OL,9,Fdeath" a coroner has ruled - and he's
OL,10,Fwarned of more deaths in the future
OL,11,Funless action is taken.
OL,13,FDiabetic Daphne Austin was admitted to
OL,14,Fthe Cumberland Infirmary in Carlisle
OL,15,Fon 22 May 2023 following a stroke.
OL,17,FWhile in hospital, she became
OL,18,Fdehydrated and by 14 June had
OL,19,Fsustained an acute kidney injury.
