OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,FHowever, she had no blood tests on 15
OL,7,For 16 June when junior doctors were
OL,8,Ftaking industrial action and her fluid
OL,9,Fbalance was poorly monitored -
OL,10,Ffactors, the coroner said,, which
OL,11,Fcontributed to her death from sepsis
OL,12,Fon 18 June.
OL,14,FThe report said: "Whilst in hospital,
OL,15,FMs Austin's glucose levels were poorly
OL,16,Fcontrolled. She also became
OL,17,Fdehydrated. Ms Austin's fluid balance
OL,18,Fwas not monitored in an effective
OL,19,Fmanner."
