OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,FA Prevention of Future Deaths report,
OL,7,Fwritten by assistant coroner for
OL,8,FCumbria, Robert Cohen, said: "In my
OL,9,Fopinion there is a risk that future
OL,10,Fdeaths will occur unless action is
OL,11,Ftaken".
OL,13,FIt went on: "There was evidence from
OL,14,Fone of the Trust's consultants that on
OL,15,Fthe day of the strike she had to 'look
OL,16,Fafter nearly 25 patients' and that
OL,17,F'due to the junior doctor's strike on
OL,18,F14/06/2023, Mrs Austin did not receive
OL,19,Fany medical input that day'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
