OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,F"Another consultant gave evidence that
OL,7,Fdespite being listed as one of the
OL,8,Fconsultants covering the unit (in the
OL,9,Fcontingency planning evidence) he was
OL,10,Fprobably dealing with other duties on
OL,11,Fthat day.
OL,13,F"In the circumstances I am concerned
OL,14,Fthat the planning that seeks to ensure
OL,15,Fsafe levels of cover during periods of
OL,16,Findustrial action was insufficient to
OL,17,Fmeet need and that this gave rise to a
OL,18,Frisk of future deaths."
