OL,6,FThe report has been sent to the North
OL,7,FCumbria Integrated Care NHS which has
OL,8,F56 days to respond to it.
OL,10,FNorth Cumbria NHS Trust said: "We
OL,11,Foffer our sincere condolences to the
OL,12,Ffamily and friends of Mrs Austin. Our
OL,13,Finitial findings indicate that some
OL,14,Fopportunities were missed to improve
OL,15,Fthe care delivered to Mrs Austin.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
