OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,F"We have worked with the clinical team
OL,7,Fto improve the way that fluid intake
OL,8,Fis monitored and this has been
OL,9,Facknowledged by the Coroner in their
OL,10,Fruling. We are now reviewing the full
OL,11,Ffindings to consider what other
OL,12,Flessons can be learned.
OL,14,F"During any period of industrial
OL,15,Faction we do put plans in place to
OL,16,Fcover any shortages in staffing. We
OL,17,Fare sorry the Coroner felt this was a
OL,18,Ffactor on this occasion."
