OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,FIn response to the Prevention of
OL,7,FFuture Deaths Report from Cumbria
OL,8,Fcoroner Robert Cohen, Professor Philip
OL,9,FBanfield, Chair of the BMA Council,
OL,10,Fsaid: "We are really sorry this
OL,11,Fhappened.
OL,13,F"Our heartfelt condolences go out to
OL,14,FDaphne Austin's family; this is a
OL,15,Fdeath that could well have been
OL,16,Favoided. As the Coroner notes, the
OL,17,FNorth Cumbria Trust's lack of
OL,18,Fpreparation and inability to ensure
OL,19,Fsufficient staffing levels during
OL,20,Findustrial action significantly
OL,21,Fcontributed to this woman's death.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
