OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,F"This is exactly why, throughout the
OL,7,Fstrike action, the BMA consistently
OL,8,Furged NHS England to prioritise
OL,9,Fpatient safety and ensure proper
OL,10,Fplanning across hospital trusts.
OL,12,F"Throughout all strike periods, the
OL,13,FBMA made it clear that during any
OL,14,Faction taken by members, Trusts must
OL,15,Fmaintain safe and appropriate staffing
OL,16,Flevels to ensure patient safety. Cover
OL,17,Facross England was provided often by
OL,18,Fmore senior doctors ` consultants,
OL,19,Fassociate specialist doctors and
OL,20,Fspecialty doctors as well as
OL,21,Fspecialists.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
