OL,3,CPensioner died after 'neglect during
OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,F"This Trust, which received a warning
OL,7,Fnotice from the CQC following
OL,8,Finspections in August and September
OL,9,F2020 to make immediate improvements
OL,10,Ffor patient safety has a longstanding
OL,11,Fhistory of issues related to patient
OL,12,Fsafety and staffing levels, with
OL,13,Fmultiple overall CQC ratings of
OL,14,F'requires improvement'.
OL,16,F"We hope the new government will take
OL,17,Fpatient safety as seriously as doctors
OL,18,Fdo and see this avoidable death as a
OL,19,Fstark warning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
