OL,4,Cjunior doctors' strike'
OL,6,F"Our health service needs to be
OL,7,Fproperly staffed and resourced, not
OL,8,Fjust during industrial action but
OL,9,Falways, as we know there are avoidable
OL,10,Fdeaths and patients coming to harm in
OL,11,Fhospitals every day, because of
OL,12,Fconsistent understaffing, poor
OL,13,Fplanning and poor management of
OL,14,Fresources."
